1.name: Internal Lockdown
1.description: All regional shopping complexes and other various crowd gathering hotspots are temporarily shut down to reduce the spread of the virus.

2.name: Hospital Infrastructure
2.description: Invest in getting more temporary hospitals built, and expanding the capacity of existing health centers.

3.name: Awareness
3.description: Make the general public aware about the spread of the virus and the Standard Operating Procedures.

4.name: Vaccination
4.description: Invest in research for a vaccine, and on getting more and more people vaccinated.

5.name: Manpower
5.description: Train more people to help in managing hospitals, engage volunteers to give tele-counseling.

6.name: Testing
6.description: Invest in making more test kits accessible to people and screening a larger number of people.
